$$\frac{sin(x^2)}{sin(x)}&amp;gt;x,(0&amp;lt;x&amp;lt;1)$$&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="-不等式等价变形">① 不等式等价变形&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>由于 $0&amp;lt;x&amp;lt;1$ 时 $\sin x &amp;gt; 0$，两边同乘以 $\sin x$，不等式等价为&lt;br>
$$&lt;br>
\sin(x^2) &amp;gt; x \sin x&lt;br>
$$&lt;br>
进一步两边同除以 $x^2&amp;gt;0$，得到&lt;br>
$$&lt;br>
\frac{\sin(x^2)}{x^2} &amp;gt; \frac{\sin x}{x}&lt;br>
$$&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="-引入辅助函数">② 引入辅助函数&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>定义函数&lt;br>
$$&lt;br>
h(t) = \frac{\sin t}{t}, \qquad t&amp;gt;0&lt;br>
$$&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Developer Inspect Editor Tokens and Scopes 命令</title><link>https://jzjizhe.github.io/tool/developer-inspect-editor-tokens-and-scopes-%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Oct 2025 16:32:26 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://jzjizhe.github.io/tool/developer-inspect-editor-tokens-and-scopes-%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</guid><description>&lt;p>❗️&lt;strong>The note is generated by DeepSeek.&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
