 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table></description></item><item><title>推导两个一维正态分布的KL散度</title><link>https://jzjizhe.github.io/theory/%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%B4%E6%AD%A3%E6%80%81%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E7%9A%84kl%E6%95%A3%E5%BA%A6/</link><pubDate>Sat, 06 Sep 2025 23:23:21 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://jzjizhe.github.io/theory/%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%80%E7%BB%B4%E6%AD%A3%E6%80%81%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E7%9A%84kl%E6%95%A3%E5%BA%A6/</guid><description>&lt;p>设&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$&lt;br>
P(x) \sim \mathcal{N}(\mu_1, \sigma_1^2), \quad Q(x) \sim \mathcal{N}(\mu_2, \sigma_2^2)&lt;br>
$$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>定义&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$&lt;br>
D_{\mathrm{KL}}(P\lVert Q) = \int P(x) \log \frac{P(x)}{Q(x)} dx&lt;br>
$$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>则有&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$&lt;br>
\boxed{&lt;br>
D_{\mathrm{KL}}(P\lVert Q) = \ln \frac{\sigma_2}{\sigma_1} + \frac{(\sigma_1^2 - \sigma_2^2) + (\mu_1 - \mu_2)^2}{2\sigma_2^2}&lt;br>
}&lt;br>
$$&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="step-1-分布比值">Step 1. 分布比值&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>$$&lt;br>
\frac{P(x)}{Q(x)} = \frac{\sigma_2}{\sigma_1} \exp \left[ \frac{\sigma_1^2(x - \mu_2)^2 - \sigma_2^2(x - \mu_1)^2}{2\sigma_1^2\sigma_2^2} \right]&lt;br>
$$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>因此&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$&lt;br>
\log \frac{P(x)}{Q(x)} = \ln \frac{\sigma_2}{\sigma_1} + \frac{(\sigma_1^2 - \sigma_2^2)x^2 + (2\sigma_2^2\mu_1 - 2\sigma_1^2\mu_2)x + (\sigma_1^2\mu_2^2 - \mu_1^2\sigma_2^2)}{2\sigma_1^2\sigma_2^2}&lt;br>
$$&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>山坡羊 自警</title><link>https://jzjizhe.github.io/literature/%E5%B1%B1%E5%9D%A1%E7%BE%8A-%E8%87%AA%E8%AD%A6/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 Aug 2025 12:02:57 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://jzjizhe.github.io/literature/%E5%B1%B1%E5%9D%A1%E7%BE%8A-%E8%87%AA%E8%AD%A6/</guid><description>&lt;p>[元 乔吉]&lt;br>
清风闲坐，白云高卧，面皮不受时人唾。&lt;br>
乐跎跎，笑呵呵，看别人搭套项推沉磨。&lt;br>
